arStrings.szText: "Ah Bulan is in the Field of Giants. We're going there to look for him."
We hope you find him. Ah Bulan hasn’t been seen for some time.
We don’t know what you will find in the wilds, so the Council has decided to offer you some...additional aid.
These stones are ancient relics from the time of the first druid. The runes inscribed on them will protect you from the evils of this world.
Take them. Use them for good.
